org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.operators.expand

Class ExpandEmbeddingsBulk

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.operators.expand.ExpandEmbeddings
      • org.gradoop.flink.model.impl.operators.matching.single.cypher.operators.expand.ExpandEmbeddingsBulk
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PhysicalOperator

    public class ExpandEmbeddingsBulk
extends ExpandEmbeddings
    Expands an vertex along the edges. The number of hops can be specified via upper and lower bound The input embedding is appended by 2 Entries, the first one represents the path (edge, vertex, edge, vertex, ..., edge), the second one the end vertex Iteration is done with BulkIteration

        lowerBound - specifies the minimum hops we want to expand

        distinctVertexColumns - indices of distinct input vertex columns
